	<Title>比亚迪重大食物中毒事件</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2009年2月23日</ReportTime>
	<Content>
		<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e1"><Location lid="l1">深圳比亚迪公司</Location><Time tid="t1" type="relTime">2月23日</Time>所发生的<Participant sid="s1">63名员工</Participant><Denoter did="d1" type="emergency">疑似食物中毒</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e2">目前已造成<Participant sid="s2">2人</Participant><Denoter did="d2" type="stateChange">死亡</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e3"><Time tid="t3" type="timeInterval">截至24日</Time>，<Participant oid="o3">19人</Participant>仍<Denoter did="d3" type="operation">留院治疗</Denoter></Event>，<Event eid="e4">另外<Participant sid="4s">42人</Participant>已<Denoter did="d4" type="operation">出院</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence><Event eid="e5"><Participant oid="o5" type="recipient">所有患者</Participant>经<Participant sid="s5" type="agent">医护人员</Participant>的全力<Denoter did="d5" type="operation"> 救治</Denoter></Event>,目前病情稳定,<Event polarity="negative" eid="e6">均无<Denoter did="d6" type="stateChange">生命危险</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>
	</Content>
